          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-emerald-600 rounded-lg p-6 h-full">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <i class="material-icons text-emerald-400 mr-3">category</i>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Novel Length Category</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Automatically categorized from Flash Fiction to Epic Novel based on industry standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-emerald-600 rounded-lg p-6 h-full">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <i class="material-icons text-emerald-400 mr-3">bar_chart</i>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Chapter Distribution</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            See how your word counts are distributed across chapters.
            Identify your longest and shortest chapters at a glance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-emerald-600 rounded-lg p-6 h-full">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <i class="material-icons text-emerald-400 mr-3">trending_up</i>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Progress Over Time</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Track your writing velocity. See how your book has grown and stay motivated with visual progress.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
        <h4 class="text-emerald-400 font-medium mb-4">Novel Length Categories</h4>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-white font-medium">Flash Fiction</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500">0-999 words</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-white font-medium">Short Story</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500">1,000-7,499</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-white font-medium">Novelette</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500">7,500-17,499</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-white font-medium">Novella</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500">17,500-39,999</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-white font-medium">Novel</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500">40,000-99,999</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-white font-medium">Epic Novel</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500">100,000+</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ========== SECTION 5: WRITING GOALS ========== %>
<section class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 body-font">
  <div class="container px-5 py-20 mx-auto">
