        </h1>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
          Writing a book takes discipline. Notebook.ai's writing goals help you stay on track by breaking
          your big ambitions into manageable daily targets.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="material-icons text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-1">flag</i>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Daily Word Goals</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Set a target and track your progress day by day. Watch your book grow one writing session at a time.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="material-icons text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-1">timeline</i>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Deadline Tracking</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Set a deadline and see exactly how many words per day you need to hit it. Adjust as you go.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="material-icons text-emerald-500 mr-3 mt-1">local_fire_department</i>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Streak Tracking</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Build a writing habit by tracking consecutive days of hitting your goals. Don't break the chain!</p>
